Package: plantr
Title: Download Data from the 'USDA' PLANTS Web API
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Michael",
           family = "Mahoney",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "mike.mahoney.218@gmail.com",
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-2402-304X"))
Description: Functions for the retrieval of data from the USDA PLANTS Database 
    (USDA, NRCS. 2020. The PLANTS Database 
    ('<https://plants.sc.egov.usda.gov/java/>'). National Plant Data 
    Team, Greensboro, NC 27401-4901 USA.), enabling users to 
    programatically download detailed data on plant species with options to 
    filter by location, introduced status, or species range. Data is in
    the public domain.
